divs: sighting details1. i awoke at approx. 5am and looked out my bedroom window. 2. the brilliance and size made me notice it. 3. perhaps a plane, until i looked through my binoculars. 4. the object didn't move it brilliantly glowed and emitted plumes of difussed light from four sides into the night sky.it also appeared to have separataely distinguished lights with spaces of black in between - like a grid pattern. i can best be described as an elongated circle\sphere. 5. i was stunned and watched it for a half hour without it moving in the sky it only disappearedn with the morning light. i was thrilled and certain i had witnessed something inexplicable. my husband witnessed it two nights later when again on a clear night it appeared in the same location in the sky.
